---
title: BBQ Pulled Chicken & Corn Nachos with Tomato Salsa & Garlic Aioli
description: You've heard of pulled pork, but this pulled chicken is easier, faster and even tastier! With a mildly spiced tomato sauce and a
side of homemade nacho chips, this meal is a feast of colourful and delicious BBQ flavours. Eat up!

